SPACED — WEDGE (CANONICAL)

Primary Wedge
Need a private place right now? Book a room near you in minutes.

Secondary Variant
Need a place right now? Get a private room near you in minutes.

Core Moment
A user needs immediate, discreet access to a private space with minimal friction.

What This Is
A wedge.
Not the MVP.
Not the feature list.
Not the operational spec.

Purpose
Use this wedge to align:
- field testing messages
- CTA language
- first-screen copy
- product direction

Do Not
- mention specific durations in the wedge
- mention 30–60 minutes
- over-explain the concept
- broaden it into a generic marketplace for space
- dilute urgency
- dilute discretion

Notes
Duration flexibility belongs in the MVP and booking flow, not in the wedge.
The wedge must stay broad enough to pull interest, but sharp enough to communicate immediate need.

Status
LOCKED
Only change this file if real-world testing clearly proves the wedge is weak.